Winter Olympics 1992:
   Games Stats: Bobsledding
Number of turns in the bobsled track at the Albertville
Games: 19.
                                                                                                       

   Jamaican bobsled team's only record: "Hobbin and Bobbin"
(recorded in 1988).
                                                                                                       

   Maximum legal weight of a four-man sled (including crew):
1,338 lbs.
                                                                                                       

   Commonest illegal bobsledding practice: coating runners
with silicone.
                                                                                                       

   Compiled by Olympics Factbook, Visible Ink Press, a
division of Gale Research, Detroit